These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
Game: snooker, mah-jongg, domino, billiard
Transport: boat, bus, roller, tram
Hobby: card-games, gardening, chess, reading
Flower: tulip, balloon-flower, aconite, orchid
 1. Transport:boat is on the right of Transport:bus##1
 2. Game:snooker is in an even position##4
 3. Hobby:card-games is on the left of Transport:roller##1
 4. Hobby:chess is on the right of Game:billiard##1
 5. Transport:boat is on the left or right of Transport:bus##3
 6. Flower:tulip is on the left of Game:mah-jongg##1
 7. Hobby:gardening == Game:domino##1
 8. Flower:aconite is in an even position##4
 9. Flower:tulip is between Flower:orchid and Transport:tram##2
10. Game:snooker == Flower:orchid##1
11. Transport:roller == Game:billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Game          | domino  | snooker    | billiard    | mah-jongg   |
| Transport   | bus     | boat   | roller       | tram    |
| Hobby   | gardening | card-games | reading    | chess |
| Flower           | balloon-flower | orchid       | tulip | aconite     |

